thread.title: AnneMarie Pirelli

author: AnneMarie Pirelli
title: AnneMarie Pirelli
text: I was originally enticed by a 50% off offer. Designing Wedding Thank You Cards with photos was a chore I was not looking forward to and had put off long enough. Your site was easy to use, had lots of design options, the final printed quality was beyond what I expected and even the packaging was great. I may have come for the price but I'll be back for the quality!
